      "content": "i get that, but like, i'm not talking about getting drunk or anything. just like a tiny bit of wine to take the edge off the anxiety so the pill works better. i've heard people do it all the time and they're fine. if it's just a little bit, is it really that much of a big deal? it's just to help me drift off.",
